snippet.title: Best VGM 2011 - The Binding of Isaac - Peace Be With You
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1173 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L8TEsGhBOfI
Best VGM 1489 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P3oYGDwIKbc

OST available here : http://dbsoundworks.bandcamp.com/album/the-binding-of-isaac-2/

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
The Binding of Isaac (2011)
Peace Be With You
Danny Baranowsky (dB)
